<p>
<h3>Introduction - What's Carmen?</h3>
<p>
Welcome to CARMEN, the Carnegie Mellon Robot Navigation
Toolkit. CARMEN is an open-source collection of software for mobile robot
control. CARMEN is modular software designed to provide basic
navigation primatives including: base and sensor control, logging,
obstacle avoidance, localization, path planning, and mapping.
<p>
<!--
The software is currently in alpha-release.  Expect to find bugs, and
