-->

See our list showing the <a href="core_functionality.html">core functionalities</a> inside Carmen.
<p>


Communications between CARMEN programs is handled using a separate
package called IPC, Copyright 1991 Christopher Fedor and Reid Simmons.
IPC is distributed along with CARMEN, however it is a separate
software development. In addition, the xr4000 module was based on
GPLed code by <a href="http://robot.anu.edu.au/~david/">David
Austin</a> for controlling the Nomadic Technologies XR4000. 

